h3 Login As {{user.email}}

div.text-center
  .btn.btn-primary(ng-click="getToken()" ng-show="!token") Get Link
p.text-center(ng-show="token" ng-click="loginAs()")
   a(href="{{loginUrl}}") Click to login
p.text-center(ng-show="token") This link will only work once. Any previously generated links will be invalidated.
p.text-center(ng-show="token") Unless you open the link in another browser/incognito window you will be logged out.
